<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Issue - <%= donorName %>
    </title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f7fa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            background: #4a6fa5;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .logo {
            height: 60px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .church-name {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 10px 0 5px;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .church-motto {
            font-style: italic;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-top: 0;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .receipt-details {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #4a6fa5;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;
        }

        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            min-width: 120px;
            color: #4a6fa5;
        }

        .thank-you {
            font-size: 18px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .verse {
            font-style: italic;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            margin: 25px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            border-top: 1px dashed #ddd;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #ddd;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #a3c4ff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .receipt-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #4a6fa5;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 15px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }

            .detail-row {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .detail-label {
                margin-bottom: 5px;
            }
        }

        .action-required {
            background-color: #fff8e6;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;
        }

        .action-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #e74c3c;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 15px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="../../public/logo.png" alt="Church Logo" class="logo">
            <div class="church-name">Ethiopian Full Gospel Believers Church (Silver Spring Local)</div>
            <div class="church-motto">Serving Christ Together</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h1>Payment Processing Issue</h1>
            <p>Dear <%= donorName %>,</p>

            <p>We wanted to let you know that we encountered an issue processing your recent <% if (isRecurring) { %>
                    recurring <% } %>donation of <%= currency %>
                            <%= amount.toFixed(2) %>.</p>

            <div class="action-required">
                <h3>Action Required</h3>
                <% if (willRetry) { %>
                    <p>We'll automatically retry this payment on <strong>
                            <%= nextRetryDate %>
                        </strong>. To ensure your donation goes through, please update your payment method below.</p>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <p>Please update your payment information to continue your support.</p>
                        <% } %>

                            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
                                <a href="<%= updatePaymentUrl %>" class="action-btn">Update Payment Method</a>
                            </div>

                            <p>Or you can <a href="<%= hostedInvoiceUrl %>">view the invoice here</a> for more details.
                            </p>
            </div>

            <p>If you believe this is an error or need any assistance, please reply to this email or contact us at
                giving@efgbcssl.org.</p>

            <div class="verse">
                "And my God will meet all your needs according to the riches of his glory in Christ Jesus."<br>
                - Philippians 4:19
            </div>

            <p>With gratitude,</p>
            <p>
                <strong>Pastor Fitsum Yab</strong><br>
                Grace Community Church
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                Ethiopian Full Gospel Believers Church (Silver Spring Local)<br>
                914 Silver Spring Ave, Suite 204 B, Silver Spring, MD 20910, USA
            </div>
            <div>
                <a href="mailto:giving@efgbcssl.org">giving@efgbcssl.org</a> |
                <a href="tel:+12408210361">(240) 821-0361</a> |
                <a href="https://efgbcssl.org">efgbcssl.org</a>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-top: 15px; opacity: 0.8;">
                This receipt may be used for tax purposes. No goods or services were provided in exchange for
                this
                donation.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>